@startuml
title Custom Codex Agent - Engine Selection & Retry Flow

actor User
participant "Frontend (app.js)" as UI
participant "API Routes (api_routes.py)" as API
participant "Run Orchestrator" as RunOrc
participant "Workflow Orchestrator" as WorkOrc
participant "Run Store (SQLite)" as Store
participant "Engine Factory" as Factory
participant "Engine Adapter (Gemini/Codex)" as Adapter

== Engine Selection (New Run) ==
User -> UI: Select Engine (Gemini/Codex)
User -> UI: Input Prompt & Execute
UI -> API: POST /api/runs { engine, prompt, ... }
API -> RunOrc: create_run(..., engine)
RunOrc -> Store: create_run(..., engine)
RunOrc -> Factory: get_adapter(engine)
Factory -> Adapter: Initialize
RunOrc -> Adapter: execute_run(prompt)
Adapter --> User: Output Results

== Engine-Aware Retry Flow ==
User -> UI: Click Retry (Current UI Engine: Gemini)
UI -> API: POST /api/runs/{id}/retry { engine: "gemini" }
API -> RunOrc: retry_run(id, engine="gemini")
RunOrc -> Store: get_run(id)
Store --> RunOrc: Original Record (e.g., engine="codex")
RunOrc -> RunOrc: create_run(..., engine="gemini")
note right: UI의 현재 선택이\n기존 기록보다 우선함
RunOrc -> Store: create_run(new_id, ..., engine="gemini")
RunOrc -> Factory: get_adapter("gemini")
RunOrc -> Adapter: execute_run(prompt)

== Workflow Step Retry ==
User -> UI: Click Retry from Step (UI Engine: Gemini)
UI -> API: POST /api/workflow-runs/{id}/retry-from-step { engine: "gemini", ... }
API -> WorkOrc: retry_workflow_run_from_step(..., engine="gemini")
WorkOrc -> WorkOrc: _restart_workflow_from_existing_run(..., engine="gemini")
WorkOrc -> WorkOrc: create_workflow_run(..., engine="gemini")
WorkOrc -> RunOrc: create_run(..., engine="gemini")
RunOrc -> Adapter: execute_step_run()

@enduml
